If you talk to any health agency as such,

00:29:55.239 --> 00:29:57.959
they're not going to say you have to restrict yourself

00:29:57.959 --> 00:30:02.680
to R or SAS or this is bad or that is good or that is better.

00:30:02.680 --> 00:30:06.359
We just have to prove it to them that what we ran whenever,

00:30:07.160 --> 00:30:09.400
when they come and ask you for evidence,

00:30:09.400 --> 00:30:12.599
that we will be able to show the exact same results

00:30:12.599 --> 00:30:14.119
with the exact same study.

