No, I really appreciate hearing that.

00:30:28.040 --> 00:30:28.920
I think it's impressive.

00:30:28.920 --> 00:30:33.239
Both really enjoy hearing about the technological pieces,

00:30:33.239 --> 00:30:35.239
but also about how the organization got there.

00:30:35.239 --> 00:30:38.119
I think it's pretty impressive that the quality

00:30:38.119 --> 00:30:40.199
and rig folks have got on board

00:30:40.199 --> 00:30:41.319
and you've been able to wrap that

00:30:41.319 --> 00:30:43.479
in all the appropriate change control

00:30:43.479 --> 00:30:47.160
and quality process stuff that they require.

00:30:47.160 --> 00:30:49.000
So yeah, it's neat to hear all this.

